{"author":"Joe Oakhart","author_email":"joeoakhart+bot@navapbc.com","author_id":"594c-9dcf-5ad6-4e6d","data":{"body":"Audit setup progress: searched for an existing architecture/OSS audit and created this task when none fit. Recorded read-only file impact. First plan-review attempt exposed the missing `[agents]` extra; remediated with the documented local `.venv` path and verified the pre-commit hook. Split the compound acceptance criterion per deterministic P6 coaching. Second review reached the live provider but returned INDETERMINATE because ANTHROPIC_API_KEY (and alternative provider credentials) are unset in this session. Per the mandatory gate protocol, the ticket remains open and unclaimed; no production-code audit has started. Next step: operator supplies a supported model credential in the execution environment, then re-run `rebar review-plan 1d3c-547d-f0cf-426c` until signed PASS and `rebar claim 1d3c-547d-f0cf-426c --assignee Codex`."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1784138818048306001,"uuid":"7fd30cf0-6ea3-4e9a-b072-2877af199c2e"}